$ git init
$ git add <file>
$ git status (status or change treeg)
$ git commit (commit changes to index)
$git push (send to your repo)
$ git pull (auto download/update all files and foldera with changes )

$ touch ...filename.ext...

it is advisable to create your diff proj in another folder other than master(default) before combining all projs in master

